                    <h2 style="font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2857; color: #333;">
                        Man New-Collection</h2>
                    <h1 style="font-size: 60px; line-height: 1.2857; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #333; padding: 19px 0px 43px 0px;">
                        JACKETS & CORTS</h1>
                    <a href="/product/shop" class="user-btn" style="padding: 10px 15px; line-height: 1.466667; background-color: #717FE0;">SHOP NOW</a>
